short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Lets you choose a free hi-resolution photo from the Unsplash.com blog and preview them on the current tab.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Lets you choose a photo from the Unsplash.com blog, and preview them to the entire page or a specified CSS selector to see how it looks. Useful when you're designing a website and want to quickly find a free image that will look good.
